                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማርያም፡</foreign>
                  </seg>
                  <desc>The word God is rubricated in the first three works; the word Mary is rubricated in the final two works. Occasionally the word God is rubricated in alternating red and black letters (e.g., <locus target="#16v #18v" facs="021 023">fols. 16v, 18v</locus>)</desc>
                  <desc>Columetric layout of text: <locus target="#119v" facs="124">fols. 119v, </locus> (Ps. 150), <locus target="#128v #129r" facs="133 133">128v, 129r</locus> (tenth biblical canticle).</desc>
                  </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
