                    <locus target="#iv(recto)" facs="004">Fol. iv(recto)</locus>
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    Record of secondary ownership and gift,
                    <q>This Psalter belongs to Alemu Gäbrä Yoḥannǝs and is given as a gift to the church of Bä‘alä Wäld</q>, written in blue ink
                    </desc>
                    </item>
